metadata.dc:description: A ureterocele in an adult patient is described. The characteristic clinical features of this condition associated with pyeloureteral duplicity and several secondary disorders make it an unusual case. The clinical features and treatment are described. The etiologic aspects are discussed, highlighting the acquired factors, as well as the diagnostic and therapeutic procedures.
metadata.dc:title: Duplicidad pieloureteral con ureterocele ortotópico complicado.
[Pieloureteral duplication with complicated orthotopic ureterocele].
